      "description": "The Caves are the starting area of SULFUR and can be entered through the cave entrance located to the left of the Church.\n\nThe Caves contain seven stages. Stage four always contains a checkpoint to refill The Amulet, and Stage seven contains the area boss, Cousin. Defeating Cousin unlocks The Town.\n\nThis area features large rooms with high ceilings, narrow bridges, and cliff ledges. The cliff ledges do significant damage to the player if they fall into one, and can outright kill the player if their health is low.",
