      "pois": [
        "Stage 4 of the Caves contains a checkpoint to refill The Amulet.",
        "Stage 5 contains a mini-boss fight, in which you have to defeat a Matryoshka Monstrosity Goblin Barrel Boy. A Scroll or Oil will occur as the reward after beating them.",
        "Stage 7 contains the area Boss, Cousin. A wooden cargo elevator will bring you back to The Church after defeating him."
      ],
      "tips": [
        "The Caves can be navigated quickly and enemies are typically grouped together closely, making the area a good choice for leveling weapon ranks.",
        "Loot containers can spawn underwater, and in hard-to-reach areas, so exploration will be frequently rewarded."
      ]
